    "Description": "Need someone to snag some cargo for us. We were using an old Hathor PAF for dead drops, but a local gang has dug in and we can\u2019t get our shit.\n\nIf you feel like kicking some ass, grab the cargo from the freight elevator at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> and deliver it to the freight elevator at <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address)</EM4>. \n\nFrom what I\u2019ve heard this place is full of all sorts. Won\u2019t be easy getting out stuff back, but that\u2019s what we\u2019re paying you for.\n\nJust make sure you got a ship that can handle a <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize)</EM4> load, and try not to get shot in the process. A <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> would also be smart to bring along. \n\nStows out.",
